original_title: Billy Blanks' Tae Bo: Total Body Fat Blaster
overview: Banish flab from every part of your body by taking-and keeping-it off once and for all with these rapid-fire moves, high-energy music and Billy 's uniquely effective motivation. You won't find a better total-body workout anywhere else, because he brings together all the weapons in his powerful TAE BO arsenal to help say goodbye to unsightly fat for good!
title: Billy Blanks' Tae Bo: Total Body Fat Blaster
